abindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bed1665703061378.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bed1665703061378.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bed1665703061378.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bed1665703061378\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n DSP Widget Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40829e1_d40830e1_d40831e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jdo1665702650723.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jdo1665702650723.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the labels (that is, the representation of a ValRep value) for radio group buttons appear to the Left or Right (default) of the buttons.\">Alignment or Text Position (align)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40832e1_d40833e1_d40834e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xgz1665703061446.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgz1665703061446.html\" title=\"DSP widget property that specifies one or more CSS files that are required to style the DSP widget.\">CSS</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40835e1_d40836e1_d40837e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nbs1665703061514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbs1665703061514.html\" title=\"DspContainer widget property that defines the name of the DSP component to embed in the DspContainer.\">Component Name (componentname)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40838e1_d40839e1_d40840e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qcz1665702650794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qcz1665702650794.html\" title=\"Number of columns used to display the options in the radio group. Default is 1.\">Number of Columns (Columns)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40841e1_d40842e1_d40843e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"psx1665702650863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/psx1665702650863.html\" title=\"Number of rows used to display the options in this radio group.\">Number of Rows ( rows)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40844e1_d40845e1_d40846e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euq1665702592938.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euq1665702592938.html\" title=\"DSP widget property that determines whether HTML code in the field is interpreted and formatted (True), or is displayed as plain text (False).\">Raw HTML (rawhtml)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40847e1_d40848e1_d40849e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sim1665702589606.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sim1665702589606.html\" title=\"DSP widget property that determines whether the browser sends requests to the server when the field holds syntactically incorrect data. True or False\">Syntax Check on Browser (ClientSyntaxCheck)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40850e1_d40851e1_d40852e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybr1665702594412.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybr1665702594412.html\" title=\"DSP widget property that determines whether the buttons of a radio group on a DSP are ordered vertically (that is, from top to bottom). True or False (default).\">Vertical Order (verticalorder)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40853e1_d40854e1_d40855e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fjp1665702589680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fjp1665702589680.html\" title=\"The name of a class to be dynamically added to (or removed from) the list of classes specified by the class attribute of a bound HTML element.\">class:ClassName</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vlc1665703063465.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vlc1665703063465.html\" title=\"DSP widget property that sets the type attribute of the HTML input element that is bound to the widget. Any type supported by the HTML standard is allowed. If a browser does not support a given type, the text type is used.\">html:type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40859e1_d40860e1_d40861e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sms1665702756004.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sms1665702756004.html\" title=\"Custom attribute that is applied to an element in the HTML layout of a Dynamic Server Page component to bind it to a definition in the Mobile App Layout framework.\">data-uniface-role</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bed1665703061378__li_d40862e1_d40863e1_d40864e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tbr1665702589761.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tbr1665702589761.html\" title=\"Causes occurrences retrieved from the server to be incrementally rendered in a dynamic server page using the specified batch sizes.\">RenderingIncrement</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612083\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612083\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DSP Widget Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DSP Widget Properties Alignment or Text Position (align) CSS Component Name (componentname) Number of Columns (Columns) Number of Rows ( rows) Raw HTML (rawhtml) Syntax Check on Browser (ClientSyntaxCheck) Vertical Order (verticalorder) class:ClassName html:type data-uniface-role RenderingIncrement Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}